azv_dag <- dagify(
    V ~  OC + OH + AS + PB,
    AE ~ OC + OH + AS + V,
    OC ~ OH + AS + PB,
    OH ~ OC + AS,
    PB ~ OH + AS + OC,
  exposure = "V",
  outcome = "AE",
  latent = c("PB"),
  labels = c(
             V = "vaccination", 
             OC = "COVID infection",
             OH = "health",
             PB = "pandemic behavior",
             AS = "age & sex", 
             AE = "adverse effect"),
   coords = list(  # Define coordinates inside dagify
    x = c(V = 0, AE = 3,  OC = 2, OH = 1, AS = 1.5, PB = 1.5),
    y = c(V = 1.4, AE = 1.4,  OC = 2, OH = 2, AS = 0.8, PB = 0)
  )
)

p <- ggdag_status(azv_dag, use_labels = "label", text = FALSE) +
  guides(fill = "none", color = "none") +  # Disable the legend
  theme_dag()
ggsave( "dag.pdf", p)
## Saving 7 x 5 in image
p

print(impliedConditionalIndependencies(azv_dag))
ggdag_paths(azv_dag) + theme_dag()

ggdag_adjustment_set(azv_dag) +theme_dag()

azv_dag <- dagify( V ~ HC + HH + OC + OH + AS + PB, AE ~ HC + HH + OC + OH + AS + V, HC ~ HH + OH + AS + PB, OC ~ HH + OH + AS + PB, HH ~ HC + OC + AS, OH ~ HC + OC + AS, exposure = V, outcome = AE, latent = c(HH,HC,PB), labels = c( V = vaccination, HC = unbserved COVID, OC = observed COVID, HH = unbserved health, OH = observed health, PB = pandemic behavior, AS = age & sex, AE = adverse effect), coords = list( # Define coordinates inside dagify x = c(V = 0, AE = 3, HC = 1, OC = 2, HH = 2.3, OH = 1, AS = 1.5, PB = 0.3), y = c(V = 1.4, AE = 1.4, HC = 0, OC = 2, HH = 0, OH = 2, AS = 0.8, PB = 0) ) )
